c: 59
v: 9
t: "Naho ba bandi batuye iki gihugu (cya Madina) mbere yabo, bahisemo ukwemera banakunda abimutse babagana, kandi mu mitima ntibararikire ibyo (abo bimukira) bahawe, ahubwo bagaharira abandi bo biretse, kabone n’ubwo na bo ubwabo babaga babikeneye. Kandi abarinzwe kugira ubugugu ni bo bazatsinda"